fair; Los Angeles 61 partly cloudy; Phoenix 83 fair; Salt Lake City
50 partly cloudy; San Diego 64 cloudy; San Francisco 56 fair;
Seattle 53 fair.
   _Canada: Montreal 63 partly cloudy; Toronto 59 cloudy.
