<HEAD>Want A Debate Ticket? Take Your Chances In Lottery</HEAD>
<DATELINE>OMAHA, Neb. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Nebraska newspapers are holding lotteries to
select who will get a limited number of tickets to next month's
