<HEAD>Africa Negotiations To Resume Next Week</HEAD>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   U.S.-mediated talks on achieving a withdrawal
of all foreign forces from southwest Africa resume next week in the
Congolese capital of Brazzaville, the State Department said
